{"tid":2118067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共国务院通過  明年起每年1月10日設中国人民警察节","createTime":"2020-07-21T08:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T15:52:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c14cb77ce081f58f9c81d03b95f18995cc41d033","tid":2118067,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"國務院早前通過公安部申請設立中國人民警察節，同意自2021年起，日期定於每年1月10日。中央政府網站周二（21日）發布國務院的批核文件稱，國務院已於本月11日批核，該節的具體工作安排將由公安部組織。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，2010年全國兩會期間，曾有人大代表建議將每年1月20日設立為人民警察節，紀念8位在海地地震中遇難的維和警察。朱曉平、郭寶山、王樹林等8人被追封為烈士，按規定家屬可享有撫卹。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200721/bkn-20200721160013392-0721_00952_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5e45f33b5381de85e3cfb97e51706125fb0053a9","tid":2118067,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69702f4143d0ce5994517c570b2e111b0e2f120d","tid":2118067,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"都關我地事 香港無警察"},{"pid":"719c69ae42fcd5f4d0070960ff386828e1dd991c","tid":2118067,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:11:28.000Z","msg":"中國警察同公安有咩分別?"},{"pid":"e19c61bb2ce8114c0ca376203c63ffbd8bbcdd53","tid":2118067,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:13:56.000Z","msg":"香港使唔使慶祝？每年1月10日去各大警署開香檳放煙花？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1babff9c3149b73444a4b014adaa72d9b717466","tid":2118067,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65dcf3fc0deae3f13ea8c39ce953db2fe248f14","tid":2118067,"uid":